WEBVTT

00:05:26.732 --> 00:05:32.427
Maelezo ya kiumbe anayesikia yanatokana
na muunganiko wa tabia

00:05:32.451 --> 00:05:35.828
za kila sauti ninayotengeneza
inakua nayo.

00:05:38.804 --> 00:05:40.317
[Sauti inasafiri]

00:05:40.341 --> 00:05:45.601
Nasafirisha katika sauti ndogo,
kama vile sauti ya gari,

00:05:46.410 --> 00:05:49.339
nguvu ya mrindimo wa muziki,

00:05:49.363 --> 00:05:50.957
ili sauti inaweza safiri.

00:05:52.313 --> 00:05:53.698
[Sauti inatenda.]

00:05:53.722 --> 00:05:55.641
Na kama kwa mchezaji katika jukwaa,

00:05:55.665 --> 00:05:59.895
sauti itatengeneza njia katika hewa.